My 1 year old and my 4 year old LOVE Sago Mini Games! We own them all and this one will be installed on my phone and our Nabi for a "last" christmas gift when the day winds down. I played it already and it's truly as cute as they said. I love the counting aspect since that's one of the skills both of my children are working on. I HIGHLY RECOMMEND FOR PARENTS OF SPECIAL NEEDS as well. My 4 year old has a speech impediment and delay and these games have really helped her grow and my 1 year old plays too!
